summary: An Ordinance providing for the refunding of a certain assessment on a portion of Tract One Hundred Sixty-one (161), Replat of J. J. McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle and part of J. J. McGilvra's Second Addition to the City of Seattle, levied for the improvement of Lake Washington District of the North Trunk Sewer, in Local Improvement District No. 1534, and heretofore cancelled by Ordinance No. 28655.
